        "id": "docling_PPT_MMAT5390Lecture1_page_023_2",
        "observed_type": "list_item",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "A 2D (grayscale) digital image is a 2D function defined on a 2D domain (usually rectangular domain):",
        "bbox": [
          0.07703490333978781,
          0.20138888928342355,
          0.9447674206427704,
